Rinascente to Become Global, Central Retail CEO Tells Corriere

-- B y   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i
-- 
2011-05-29T10:10:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/rinascente-to-become-global-central-retail-ceo-tells-corriere.html
Thailand ’s Central Retail Corp. Ltd.
plans to strengthen La Rinascente brand and make it global,
Chief Executive Officer Tos Chirathivat told  Corriere della Sera 
in an interview.  New openings are planned in Venice and Rome, Chirathivat
told the newspaper, adding that the company will export the
brand to the major cities of Eastern Europe, Middle East and
 China .  Central Retail Corp.’s goal is to place La Rinascente among
the first five luxury department-store chains in the world, the
newspaper quoted the CEO as saying.  La Rinascente SpA investors approved a sale of the company
to Central Retail Corp. on May 27.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francesca Cinelli in Milan at 
 fcinelli@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Ludden at   jludden@bloomberg.net  